text: Grafenried was a municipality in the administrative district of Bern- Mittelland in the canton of Bern in Switzerland. On 1 January 2014, the former municipalities of Grafenried, Büren zum Hof, Etzelkofen, Limpach, Mülchi, Schalunen and Zauggenried merged into the municipality of Fraubrunnen. ==Other websites== Category:Former municipalities in Bern-Mittelland
title: Grafenried, Switzerland
